            <div class="orghub-faq-grid">
                <article><h3>What can I do with PDF organizer tools?</h3><p>You can merge, split, reorder, rotate, delete, extract, and crop PDF pages.</p></article>
                <article><h3>Can I reorder PDF pages?</h3><p>Yes. Use Organize PDF to arrange pages into the sequence you need.</p></article>
                <article><h3>Can I split a large PDF?</h3><p>Yes. Use Split PDF to create smaller files from page ranges.</p></article>
                <article><h3>Can I delete pages permanently?</h3><p>Yes. Delete PDF Pages creates a new output file without the removed pages. Review the download before sharing.</p></article>
                <article><h3>Do I need an account?</h3><p>Most organizer workflows are available without signup for standard files.</p></article>
                <article><h3>Are files stored?</h3><p>Files are processed securely and deleted within the normal retention window.</p></article>
